    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "calling 911 seems like a lot for just being winded when i walk around the house. it's probably just my lungs getting old and i'm just overreacting. if i just take an extra dose of the inhaler and maybe some of my old cough syrup it'll settle down, right? i don't want to go to the hospital if i don't have to.",
