      "content": "Taking an extra dose of your inhaler and some cough syrup might give you temporary relief, but it's not a long-term solution. Your lungs may be aging, but they still need proper care. If you're feeling winded, it's not just about age—it's about making sure you're taking the right steps to manage your asthma. If you're not sure, it's always better to consult a doctor. They can provide a safe and effective treatment plan for you.",
